name: "Plain Is Money" Black Hoodie 14K
description: AV Clothing is a dynamic company with clothing like no other. AV Clothing offers high end clothes with the signature 14k Pure Gold AV emblem. All gold is 100% authenticated. AV started in Hamilton, Ontario. I'm just a man with a big dream. After countless months of designing and marketing, we've finally been cleared to launch. This here is the first collection of the AV "Plain is Money" Fall Line. This hoodie is a cotton-fleece blend. Both the left chest and left sleeve will have the 14k Emblem on the side. A booklet will be sent along with the hoodie to give instructions on how to wash and maintain the quality of it.
